- This way, please. 
 - Young Master...

56
00:08:52,460 --> 00:08:54,860
- You have to catch Young Master Eight's shadow plays. 
 - Welcome.

57
00:08:54,860 --> 00:08:58,990
- This way, please! 
 - Step right in, everyone.

58
